plt.figure(figsize = (15,15))
plt.subplot(141)
plt.imshow(image, cmap = 'gray')

plt.subplot(142)
fft_image = np.fft.fft2(image)
plt.imshow(1 + np.log(np.abs(1 + fft_image)), cmap='gray')

# (-1)*(x+y)  [tmp_fft_image]
plt.subplot(143)
tmp_image = np.zeros_like(image)
for i in range(image.shape[0]):
    for j in range(image.shape[1]):
        tmp_image[i][j] = image[i][j] * np.power(-1,i + j)
tmp_fft_image = np.fft.fft2(tmp_image)
plt.imshow(np.abs(tmp_fft_image))

plt.subplot(144)
plt.imshow((1 + np.log(np.abs(tmp_fft_image))),cmap = 'gray')
